{"tid":417500,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[純文字]悠二砌機買料有感","createTime":"2017-09-28T17:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T11:39:15.000Z","uid":52656,"like":20,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"54c2bce1e7eb61071b7f2a48aadde31253f5fd66","tid":417500,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"由於早前有朋友搵我幫手砌機<br />\n於是我就幫佢搵條LIST<br />\n而最近收到風悠二正式開鋪<br />\n所以今次就試下搵佢買野<br />\n由於今日即興砌機,而且BUDGET有限<br />\n所以我先打比悠二問D料齊唔齊咁<br />\n之後就開始搵料<br />\n由於悠二話好多野唔係佢間鋪,要去倉拎,而我又成18:30先到 (好似佢地收19:00)<br />\n所以冇計啦,有D料就要去番大鋪買<br />\n<br />\nLIST:<br />\nCPU: R5 1600 $1630 (悠二) <br />\nM/B: AsRock AB350M-PRO4 $590 (中田)<br />\nRam: G.SKILL AEGIS GAMING SERIES 16GB (2 X 8GB) DDR4 3000MHZ C16 F4-3000C16D-16GISB $1250 (悠二)<br />\nDISPLAY: ZOTAC GTX1080 MINI $4050 (中田)<br />\nHDD: TOSHIBA 3TB $530 (悠二)<br />\nP/S: NEOECO2 550W $540 (悠二)<br />\nCASE: SHARKOON 勁風者 VG5-W ATX $320 (悠二)<br />\nSSD: SAMSUNG PM961 POLARIS 256GB M.2 PCIE NVME 3.0 X4 $855 (悠二)<br />\n$9765<br />\n<br />\n雖然有D野悠二係會貴幾十蚊(但唔少都平過黃金)<br />\n但問題係佢地可以包運貨<br />\n同埋你打過去有人會比D意見你點樣砌好,同埋佢都真係有睇下D PRODUCT D 料,真係幾熟,大慨都知咩牛係邊間野代工,某D 款 D QC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (不過我覺得有時將貨就價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但怕重又唔急又住係大西北既朋友其實都係一個非常好既選擇<br />\n黃金價錢仲要送埋上門<br />\n同埋如果一部機砌埋個價錢都同出面都差唔遠,識選料應該會平過TIM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都可以四圍格下價邊道抵屌買邊道<br />\n而悠二間鋪個位都好近MTR<br />\n係C出口一上,SHELL油站前少少就係<br />\n不過如果有心拎貨最好早一日搵佢等佢READY<br />\n因為我都係事前早2個鐘安排D 料點買同搵料<br />\n而且談話中都好好吹,又介紹下E 排 D人買RYZEN 配RAM<br />\n除左冇貨既HOF 同唔係道道都有得賣既AEGIS<br />\n都仲要其他選擇<br />\n而好好彩如佢所言,對RAM 係AGESA to 1.0.0.6b BIOS下 直上3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結: 我覺得佢地係有心做,D 野都熟同睇得出有KEEP 住UPDATE 資訊同埋都簡單化咁介紹到D 野比客知,希望佢地可以比心機做落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係希望 D 介紹D 產品可以多元化D,例如我想要隻模組牛你同我講NEOECO2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係隻好牛,但問題佢唔係模組牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n雖然我朋友唔介意同埋隻機箱都幾容易咁收線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢地KEEP住咁比心機做落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dfaf26f07d5169f07e7c9c6372111426a7176c","tid":417500,"uid":142,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"係咁以掃一掃<br />\n啲野珍寶買 平到幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7394b43925593adb6b26c9091afe14665d1f1c5","tid":417500,"uid":142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁以掃一掃<br />\n啲野珍寶買 平到幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百幾啦 冇幾舊嘅"},{"pid":"f6661eb8069f139cf5ad023f8bf3becfd59ff6a6","tid":417500,"uid":52656,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁以掃一掃<br />\n啲野珍寶買 平到幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes <br />\nRam同埋牛貴左<br />\n所以真係要格價"},{"pid":"30f6ef419d30f34e72ccca7c62312b7b79a31754","tid":417500,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁以掃一掃<br />\n啲野珍寶買 平到幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果成部機真係有機會貴<br />\n主要貴左display card <br />\n你冇計錯"},{"pid":"e5124aaeab1187c2cd03334bfdb55703e95b867c","tid":417500,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"